{"tid":981793,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"懷舊是懷舊香港　不是中國　香港人的國家是香港　不是中國","createTime":"2019-01-14T14:32:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-23T11:28:17.000Z","uid":47714,"like":202,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"82b26b833892a31f799588b35c0fd4811f2a879c","tid":981793,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T14:32:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/ZenoIndie/status/1073468132998578177\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FZenoIndie%2Fstatus%2F1073468132998578177&d=ku5Y7cvE3IkWa4GmX7CZ42i1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=dc00b9e1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FZenoIndie%2Fstatus%2F1073468132998578177&h=22c947f6\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/ZenoIndie/status/1073468132998578177</a><br />\n<br />\n我們社會，懷舊是懷舊香港，不是懷舊中國，熱愛本土不是喜愛中國，本地蛋不是中國蛋，我們對 made in Hong Kong 充滿情懷時 made in China 是另一種東西。哪裡是香港人的國家其實非常明顯，絕不是中國。我們香港人，香港利益就是我們國家利益，中國利益是敵國利益，中國是香港敵國，兩者利益是衝突的。"},{"pid":"8f65701fa0911a5480167b6c66601abfc021788c","tid":981793,"uid":47714,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T14:31:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c18425c62631473e785414a03008939086cf9f7a","tid":981793,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T14:19:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"375fdeb13d884d807921bced821c2d76a5a3b9ea","tid":981793,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T13:51:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a355cbc753563f5fa442074e477e88c6d9301eb4","tid":981793,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T13:45:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e952b765561126605cdfac2b7b904af923d6785e","tid":981793,"uid":226